      "updated": 1771590616449,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "clarify what we are solving\n    1. 2. 3.\npriorities => solve top 1\npriority system to develop\n\nscale (MEM & QPS)\nuser (latency & CP vs AP)",
