    {
      "id": "GGpqkkYCzvl3IyllSV9U8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 429.951348281189,
      "y": 195.88618903298573,
      "width": 777.4595336914062,
      "height": 700,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1566947936,
      "version": 1232,
      "versionNonce": 876473248,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771592042153,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "purpose? URL => internal use case\n\n100 million URLs are generated per day\nas short as possible\nA-Z, a-z, 0-9\n(assume read 10: 1 write)\nstore 10 years\nURL be del/ update? NO\n\nasked:\n1. whats the traffic vol\n2. how long is the shortened URL\n3. what characters are allowed to be in the URL\n4. can shortened URLs be deleted or udpated\n\n\nFUNC:\n- input longUrl, ouptput shortUrl => 1 service for generation\n- using shortUrl, query our service, redirects to the longUrl's site => redirection\n\n---OOS---\n- link analytics?\n\nNON FUNC:\n- minimize redirect latency\n- be able to store 100 mil URL/ day for 10 years\n- 1 bil read req per day\n- high availability, scalability, fault tolerance always be considered",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "purpose? URL => internal use case\n\n100 million URLs are generated per day\nas short as possible\nA-Z, a-z, 0-9\n(assume read 10: 1 write)\nstore 10 years\nURL be del/ update? NO\n\nasked:\n1. whats the traffic vol\n2. how long is the shortened URL\n3. what characters are allowed to be in the URL\n4. can shortened URLs be deleted or udpated\n\n\nFUNC:\n- input longUrl, ouptput shortUrl => 1 service for generation\n- using shortUrl, query our service, redirects to the longUrl's site => redirection\n\n---OOS---\n- link analytics?\n\nNON FUNC:\n- minimize redirect latency\n- be able to store 100 mil URL/ day for 10 years\n- 1 bil read req per day\n- high availability, scalability, fault tolerance always be considered",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1neJaPxw1zh08evixzwLc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1189.4878353510624,
      "y": 142.66904277974527,
      "width": 617.53955078125,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1083131808,
      "version": 433,
      "versionNonce": 2063859296,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771591949411,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "self notes:\nclairfication:\n- [QPS] always contextualise: dont ask write => ask generated\n- ask length of these URLs\n- [QPS] assume + clarify read: write ration 10: 1\n- [MEM] storage\n\n- non-func can also think about cache, s\n\n- i guess can ask if they want the URL quickly\n- \"does this requirements satisfy the problem statement?\"\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "self notes:\nclairfication:\n- [QPS] always contextualise: dont ask write => ask generated\n- ask length of these URLs\n- [QPS] assume + clarify read: write ration 10: 1\n- [MEM] storage\n\n- non-func can also think about cache, s\n\n- i guess can ask if they want the URL quickly\n- \"does this requirements satisfy the problem statement?\"\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yE2k7LikYvFQH5aiXX8dB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 431.66800364750827,
      "y": 945.051469744269,
      "width": 544.2396850585938,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6c",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 245778336,
      "version": 486,
      "versionNonce": 911948384,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771592495284,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Back of the env estimations:\n[MEM]\n100 mil URLs\n~100 bytes each URL => 1 row in DB\n1 day => 100 mil * 100B = 10GBs\n1 year => 365 * 10GBs = 3.65TBs\n10 years => 36.5 TBs\n\n[QPS - write]\n100 mil URLs / day => day == ~100k secs (24 * 60*60)\n1000 write/sec\n\n[QPS - read]\n10 000 reads/sec ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of the env estimations:\n[MEM]\n100 mil URLs\n~100 bytes each URL => 1 row in DB\n1 day => 100 mil * 100B = 10GBs\n1 year => 365 * 10GBs = 3.65TBs\n10 years => 36.5 TBs\n\n[QPS - write]\n100 mil URLs / day => day == ~100k secs (24 * 60*60)\n1000 write/sec\n\n[QPS - read]\n10 000 reads/sec ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
