      "text": "CORE ENTITIES\nUsers\nlongUrl\nshortUrl\n\n\nAPI\n# getShortUrl(longUrl)\nPOST /v1/URL_gen/\n{\n    longUrl\n}\n-> shortUrl\n\n\n# get site using shortUrl; getSite(shortUrl)\nGET /v1/site_retriever?shortUrl={shortUrl}\n-> response status 302\n\n=> redirects are specifically handled by http 300 status codes\n301 vs 302\n301 - perm shift => min. rediret latency\n302 - temp. shift (default)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CORE ENTITIES\nUsers\nlongUrl\nshortUrl\n\n\nAPI\n# getShortUrl(longUrl)\nPOST /v1/URL_gen/\n{\n    longUrl\n}\n-> shortUrl\n\n\n# get site using shortUrl; getSite(shortUrl)\nGET /v1/site_retriever?shortUrl={shortUrl}\n-> response status 302\n\n=> redirects are specifically handled by http 300 status codes\n301 vs 302\n301 - perm shift => min. rediret latency\n302 - temp. shift (default)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
