      "text": "CORE ENTITIES\nUsers\nlongUrl\nshortUrl\n\n\nAPI\n# getShortUrl(longUrl)\nPOST /api/urls/shorten\nreq: Long URL\nres: Short URL\n\n# get site using shortUrl; getSite(shortUrl)\nGET /api/urls/{shortUrl}\nres: Redirect 300 (include the \n\n*300\nresponse is going to be the redirect\n& redirect will include longURL\n=> redirects are specifically handled by http 300 status codes\n301 vs 302\n301 - perm shift => min. rediret latency\n302 - temp. shift (default)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CORE ENTITIES\nUsers\nlongUrl\nshortUrl\n\n\nAPI\n# getShortUrl(longUrl)\nPOST /api/urls/shorten\nreq: Long URL\nres: Short URL\n\n# get site using shortUrl; getSite(shortUrl)\nGET /api/urls/{shortUrl}\nres: Redirect 300 (include the \n\n*300\nresponse is going to be the redirect\n& redirect will include longURL\n=> redirects are specifically handled by http 300 status codes\n301 vs 302\n301 - perm shift => min. rediret latency\n302 - temp. shift (default)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
